I want to know everything,
I want to know everything

12
00:01:09,540 --> 00:01:12,090
I can't fool you forever

13
00:01:12,090 --> 00:01:14,720
I can't keep this hidden

14
00:01:14,720 --> 00:01:19,470
I want to shout out my secret, AHHH

15
00:01:21,390 --> 00:01:23,930
Take that! Telepathy

16
00:01:23,930 --> 00:01:26,390
Te-te-te-telepathy

