"The Reason for Her Smile."

21
00:01:38,530 --> 00:01:41,580
Morning, Misuzu-chan!
Nice morning, isn't it?

22
00:01:41,580 --> 00:01:42,450
Good morning.

23
00:01:42,830 --> 00:01:45,290
Yes! She didn't ignore me today!

24
00:01:45,290 --> 00:01:46,410
And you...

25
00:01:47,410 --> 00:01:48,870
are who, again?

26
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:52,420
I'm your classmate, Tanabe!

27
00:01:55,340 --> 00:01:57,510
I really wanna see her smile.

28
00:01:57,880 --> 00:02:01,220
Misuzu-chan never smiles at all, you know?

29
00:02:01,220 --> 00:02:05,430
Nothing wrong with being expressionless,
but what would make her smile?

30
00:02:05,430 --> 00:02:08,690
What are you talking about?
She smiles all the time.

31
00:02:08,690 --> 00:02:09,900
Huh?! No way!

32
00:02:10,230 --> 00:02:13,440
In fact, she's almost always
smiling when she talks to me.

33
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:14,860
She's so damn mean-spirited.

34
00:02:15,230 --> 00:02:16,400
For real?!

35
00:02:16,740 --> 00:02:18,110
Man, I'm so jealous!

36
00:02:18,110 --> 00:02:21,200
Childhood friends have a
totally different experience!

